# Dashboard Refinements & To-Do Feature

## What Was Done

### 1. New To-Do Task Tracking Feature
A complete task management system was created with minimal-friction design for students:

**Backend:**
- [todo.py](file:///Users/oli/Desktop/LMSManager/backend/app/models/todo.py) - Todo model with priority, categories, due dates, and optional assignment linking
- [todos.py](file:///Users/oli/Desktop/LMSManager/backend/app/routes/todos.py) - Full CRUD API with toggle endpoint for quick completion

**Frontend:**
- [todo-widget.tsx](file:///Users/oli/Desktop/LMSManager/frontend/components/todos/todo-widget.tsx) - Dashboard widget with quick-add and single-click completion
- [todos page](file:///Users/oli/Desktop/LMSManager/frontend/app/todos/page.tsx) - Full task management page with filtering, stats, and modal creation

**Features:**
- Quick-add with inline form
- Priority levels (High/Medium/Low) with color coding
- Optional due dates and categories
- Single-click toggle completion (optimistic updates)
- Dashboard shows top 5 pending tasks

